  <summary date="2021-10-26T17:08:47Z" status="Introduced in House">Hiring Incentive to Return Employment Act of 2021 or the HIRE Act of 2021

This bill increases the rate of the work opportunity tax credit from 40% to 50% of wages paid to members of the targeted groups eligible for such credit over a two-year period. It also increases to $10,000 the amount of wages taken into account for purposes of the credit.</summary>
